@apiURL = https://fw-teaching.fi/demo/wdbocms/api/v1/products/
### Get all products
GET {{apiURL}}
### Get one product
GET {{apiURL}}/1002
### Create a new product
POST {{apiURL}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Sweater",
    "price": 20
}
### Update a single field in a product
PATCH {{apiURL}}/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 999
}
### Update all data
PUT {{apiURL}}/1001
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Shirt",
    "price": 40
}
### Delete a product
DELETE {{apiURL}}/1003